                <Gloss>to redeem the time</Gloss>
              </Glosses>
              <Comments>It is also possible to interpret ἐξαγοράζομαι τὸν καιρόν in {S:04900501600002} as ‘to take full advantage of every opportunity’ (see {D:65.42}).</Comments>
